[SHORT DESC]
A Ball used to catch Pokemon that is more effective against Bug- and Water-type Pokemon.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>A Ball used to catch Pokemon. Will fail during Trainer battles. Cannot be used in Link or Wi-Fi battles.</p>

<p>Net Ball has a capture rate modifier of *1. When used on a Pokemon that is <a href="/dp/types/bug">Bug</a>- or <a href="/dp/types/water">Water</a>-typed, the modifier becomes *3.</p>